title: Dick Tracy's Dilemma ( 1947) Crime Drama Starring Ralph Byrd, Lyle Latell And Kay Christopher

sources.title: Dick Tracy's Dilemma ( 1947) Crime Drama Starring Ralph Byrd, Lyle Latell And Kay Christopher
sources.description: Legendary police detective Dick Tracy (Ralph Byrd) and his faithful partner, Pat Patton (Lyle Latell), investigate the daring heist from a local warehouse of a recently insured fortune in furs. As the pair follows clues leading to shifty socialite Tess Trueheart (Kay Christopher), a growing body cou nt at the morgue hints at the possibility of a serial killer on the loose. Tracy and Patton struggle to find the killer while working to unravel this high-fashion mystery.
